805
01:03:33,769 --> 01:03:35,980
What the hell have we gotten into here?

806
01:03:36,230 --> 01:03:38,357
Yeah. Here.

807
01:03:39,274 --> 01:03:42,611
Wonder if there's an opening
in the fire department?

808
01:03:52,871 --> 01:03:54,121
Want to tell me about it?

809
01:03:54,498 --> 01:03:56,917
- About what?
- Don't bullshit me.

810
01:03:57,126 --> 01:04:00,587
Your daughter wasn't killed
for something she was into.

811
01:04:00,796 --> 01:04:03,007
She was killed for something you're into.

812
01:04:04,758 --> 01:04:05,968
Stop me if I'm wrong.

813
01:04:07,302 --> 01:04:09,388
I don't know what you mean.

814
01:04:10,514 --> 01:04:13,475
Keep your hands
away from your pocket, okay?

815
01:04:14,101 --> 01:04:15,978
- Easy, man.
- Fuck easy.

816
01:04:19,023 --> 01:04:22,443
You called me the other day
to blow the whistle, right?

817
01:04:23,152 --> 01:04:24,778
Blow the whistle on what?

818
01:04:24,945 --> 01:04:28,282
You were going to spill your guts,
so they killed your daughter.

819
01:04:28,490 --> 01:04:31,160
Tell me if I'm wrong.
