the whole thing down.

831
01:05:15,037 --> 01:05:16,872
We killed everybody.

832
01:05:21,960 --> 01:05:23,670
We also formed a plan.

833
01:05:24,088 --> 01:05:25,214
Keep talking.

834
01:05:31,470 --> 01:05:34,848
A few years ago, Shadow Company
got together again.

835
01:05:35,224 --> 01:05:36,892
The war was over.

836
01:05:37,893 --> 01:05:41,480
- But we still had our sources in Asia.
