975
01:20:22,568 --> 01:20:23,861
...then we all die.

976
01:20:25,405 --> 01:20:27,073
I don't think so.

977
01:20:28,950 --> 01:20:30,076
Daddy!

978
01:20:35,081 --> 01:20:36,874
Come on, honey.

979
01:20:38,918 --> 01:20:39,919
Just a smoker.

980
01:20:40,169 --> 01:20:41,421
Bingo.

981
01:20:46,592 --> 01:20:48,469
- Where is he?
- It's Riggs.

982
01:20:50,930 --> 01:20:53,266
Rianne, get in the car!

983
01:20:54,934 --> 01:20:56,602
Get in the fucking car!

984
01:21:14,620 --> 01:21:16,122
Go, Rianne, go!

985
01:21:16,456 --> 01:21:19,167
Come on, cottontail, stick your head up.

986
01:21:20,626 --> 01:21:23,129
That's it, you son of a bitch.
Good night.

987
01:21:26,799 --> 01:21:29,510
Don't try it, son.
You're not that fast.

988
01:21:31,512 --> 01:21:33,347
<i>Hello, Joshua. Hello, Joshua.</i>

989
01:21:33,556 --> 01:21:35,308
- Yes, sir.
<i>- I got Riggs.</i>

990
01:21:36,142 --> 01:21:38,811
He's got Riggs. Go get the girl!

991
01:22:14,222 --> 01:22:16,224
Throw your weapon down!

992
01:22:16,516 --> 01:22:18,851
Put your hands behind your head!

993
01:22:22,897 --> 01:22:26,567
You're Gen. Peter McAllister,
commander of Shadow Company.

994
01:22:27,026 --> 01:22:29,695
I see we've heard of each other.

995
01:22:29,862 --> 01:22:33,407
Yep. It'll almost be a shame
when I nail you.

996
01:22:34,367 --> 01:22:38,704
I ran into some of those Shadow Company
pussies in Saigon in '69.

997
01:22:38,996 --> 01:22:40,248
You did, did you?

998
01:23:27,420 --> 01:23:29,255
Leave me alone!

999
01:23:55,948 --> 01:23:58,284
Save your strength.
You'll need it.

1000
01:23:58,618 --> 01:23:59,619
Who's the Chin?

1001
01:24:00,828 --> 01:24:03,456
Endo, meet Mr. Martin Riggs.

1002
01:24:04,582 --> 01:24:07,501
Endo has forgotten more
about dispensing pain...

1003
01:24:07,710 --> 01:24:08,961
...than we'll ever know.

1004
01:24:09,170 --> 01:24:10,630
Terrific.

1005
01:24:10,838 --> 01:24:12,632
See, we have a problem.

1006
01:24:12,798 --> 01:24:14,634
Since we have Murtaugh...

1007
01:24:15,134 --> 01:24:16,469
...we don't need you.

1008
01:24:16,802 --> 01:24:20,139
- I believe in being thorough.
- I've heard that about you.

1009
01:24:22,350 --> 01:24:25,019
Our problem, and yours too...

1010
01:24:25,811 --> 01:24:28,814
...is we have a shipment
of merchandise to deliver.

1011
01:24:28,981 --> 01:24:30,858
Why don't you just call it heroin?

1012
01:24:32,526 --> 01:24:34,904
It's rather large, this shipment.

1013
01:24:35,863 --> 01:24:37,823
It would be unfortunate...

1014
01:24:37,990 --> 01:24:40,743
...if we showed up
to deliver our heroin...

1015
01:24:41,410 --> 01:24:43,162
...and were surrounded by 50 cops.

1016
01:24:43,371 --> 01:24:44,622
